Do you or a family member have a home that you want to sell, but it needs a major renovation?<br>
Or perhaps the house is packed full of stuff that no one wants?<br>
Or maybe it's been sitting vacant a long time waiting for the right time to get it ready to sell?<br>
<br>
You don't have to make repairs, you don't have to get it ready, and you don't even need to worry about the stuff!<br>
<br>
Our team has been helping families eliminate the hard parts of selling a house in the Kansas City Metro since 2000.  <br>
We have the team and resources to solve problems and get things done.<br>
We have been on the Top 10 Home Buyers list since about 2015.  <br>
Recently we have earned our Certified Buyer and Senior Transition Specialist Designations from Mom's House.<br>
<br>
What does that mean for you?<br>
<br>
That you can get a fair cash offer, that we can stand behind.<br>
That we can close quickly or on your time frame.<br>
That you don't have to "get the house ready".<br>
That you don't have to deal with showings and marketing.<br>
That you don't have to worry about buyer inspections or appraisals.<br>
That you can get the equity out of the house and move on.<br>
<br>
Tell us a bit about yourself and the property at http://www.kcmohomebuyer.com/craigs <br>
<br>
-----<br>
<br>
We work with people every week who need to sell their house fast.<br>
From people getting divorced or married who have a house no one wants.  To families transitioning mom or dad to Senior Housing.  And a whole host of reasons that people have a house they no longer want or need, that they don't want to deal with anymore. . . <br>
<br>
What all of these people we help have in common is. . .<br>
<br>
‚úîÔ∏è They want to be treated fair<br>
‚úîÔ∏è They need a solution fast<br>
‚úîÔ∏è They don't have the extra cash to pay all kinds of fees like real estate agent fees, closing fees, etc<br>
‚úîÔ∏è They just want out of the headache this house is giving them<br>
<br>
. . . and they've found that we can help them.<br>
<br>
We can buy quickly and eliminate the need to pay any out-of-pocket expenses to sell. Our goal is to structure an offer that is a "Win, Win" for both the buyer and seller. We never use high-pressure tactics to get you to sell us your house and we will show you the information and figures we use to calculate a fair offer for your property<br>
<br>
We'll Make You An Offer Within 24 to 48 Hours.<br>
<br>
You Decide If It's A Fit or Not. It's That Easy And Stress-Free<br>
<br>
Get a quick quote now by going to http://www.kcmohomebuyer.com/craigs and entering your property information.<br>
Our website is up and working 24-7, or you can always call during business hours at  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/ksc/apa/7505357683/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
.<br>
-------------------------------------------------------<br>
The Tuckers at kcmoHomeBuyer.com are all licensed real estate agents at Realty Resource. We are posting this ad in an effort to BUY your property, but we also have the option to list it if that would be better for YOU. We have the license, the knowledge, and the expertise to help you discuss your options and find the best one for you, be that an all-cash offer closing quickly from us or another option with us or one of our trusted partners.<br>
